{
  "stem": "24137.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the way I know it was a Saturday is because the aunt, the mother of the little boy, she said, I don't go on trucks on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Because I don't ride on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they said, well, you are getting on this truck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And again, the beating started.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And her little boy, he screamed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he cried.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And he was yelling, you know, Mama, Mama.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[CRYING] And a lot of people were screaming and crying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Because it was a place where they were separating people to go into different camps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And [CRYING] they took my two aunts and us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And they put us on these trucks, and some other people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they took us to a place called Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And in Ravensbruck, I think this other aunt that she lost her mind.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "She lost her mind because she acted very, very strange.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And whatever they told her, she was saying, I'm not getting undressed in front of men, and give me back my sheitel.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "[POINTS] And I don't want to eat non-kosher food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And I want to go home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And give me my child.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And they-- and my other aunt took the little boy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And now she was in charge of the little boy because this, this aunt was, really already, she was-- she lost her mind.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And-- [CRYING] And my aunt, the one that was OK, she said to me, I want you to hold this aunt's hand.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And whenever they tell us to go someplace, you-- you just pull her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Because I have to take care of the little boy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And I have to take care of this other little girl, of her daughter.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
